title: Modern pen drawings - European and American (1901 Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / English / 1901 The Studio, London, NY etc / 373 pages / 29 MB

Holme, Charles, 1848-1923

THE purpose of this book is a simple one, namely, to give typical and varied examples of contemporary pen-and-ink drawings. It is not intended to supply an illustrated catalogue of all the notable pen draughtsmen of Europe and America. Some well-known names will be missed, and missed with regret ; but the Editor has endeavoured, within the limits of the space at his disposal, to render each section of the book as representative as possible of the best work of the nationalities dealt with.
